    <note>Zhang(1) Qi [182] Shao's [7163] younger brother. He was given office when Shao was appointed as an ambassador to Jin in 1129. Han(1) Yuanlong's [670] father-in-law, Li Wenyuan [7043]'s son-in-law. His brother Tan's [3162] son, Xiaozhong [3142], was dismissed as Huainan yunpan in 1209. His own son, Xiaoxiang [3144], was jinshi #1 in 1154 at the age of 23. Zhang Xiaoxiang, WJ, 'fu,' 1a, 4a; Zhou Bida, WJ, 65.2b; Han Yuanji, WJ, 22.22b; XNYL, 181.10b, 182.14b, 16a, 184.5b, 185.13a, 188.6a; SHY:ZG, 70.51a, 74.33a; SHY:SH, 49.44b-45a. CBD, 3, 2240-41.</note>
